Louis appears to be confirming that the pair are smoking an illegal substance, handing his bandmate the cigarette while saying: 'One very very important factor of Zayn's warm up of course is Mary J, herself'.

The band was criticised after the video leak and bandmember Liam Payne tweeted an apology saying 'I love my boys and maybe things have gone a little sideways. I apologize for that.'

